-- Fujitsu to Own 80% of Mobile Phone Venture With Toshiba, Nikkei Reports
-- Tak Kumakura
-- 2010-07-28T22:14:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-28/fujitsu-to-own-80-of-mobile-phone-venture-with-toshiba-nikkei-reports.html

          
          
             Fujitsu Ltd., which agreed to form a
mobile-phone venture with Toshiba Corp., will own 80 percent of
the new company, the Nikkei newspaper reported, without saying
where it obtained the information.   
 The venture will have 300 workers. The companies will
announce the plan today, the newspaper said.  
          
          


  


        